OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fmove northeast across Scotland
OL,7,Fovernight, with some outbreaks
OL,8,Fdeveloping across northern England and
OL,9,Finitially Northern Ireland. Mostly dry
OL,10,Felsewhere, though generally becoming
OL,11,Frather cloudy. A rather warm night,
OL,12,Fexcept across northeast Scotland, with
OL,13,Fmostly light winds too.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FSome showery outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain will affect northern and western
OL,17,Fareas on Tuesday. Otherwise it looks
OL,18,Flargely dry with some warm spells of
OL,19,Fsunshine, and mostly light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
